{"tid":2316299,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[請推上熱門] 咪撚慣 一慣就死得","createTime":"2020-12-07T19:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T02:44:10.000Z","uid":251732,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"795a8989a75036d59152041a36d6cefa4483fe31","tid":2316299,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T19:34:00.000Z","msg":"大家好，我是Edward。2019年的12月8日，對其他人可能是很普通的一天，但對我們整隊屠龍，那天是改變了我們命運的一天，因為那天正是我們覆滅的日子。<br />\n當日的經歷，直到此時此刻都還歷歷在目，那天我正打算睡覺的時候，我聽到我門外有一陣聲響，我立刻望向防盜眼，發現有多名大漢在我門前像賊人一樣破壞我家門，不到10秒鐘，我家大門被那多名大漢破開，我第一時間看到的是一名大漢手持一把手槍指向我，其他幾名大漢衝過來把我制服，直到那時我才知道那數名大漢是警察，然後驚動了我的家人，但我的家人有老人家，那數名警員還一直出言恐嚇。<br />\n回到警署，我看到數個熟悉的身影後才得知，其他隊友也全數被捕，當時我認為應該這次逃不掉了，在萬念俱灰的情況底下我已經做好最壞的打算，想了一想，坐監也不是最壞的事，比起無緣無故失去生命的人，自己算是好了一點，因為我還可以在監獄中好好學習，裝備好自己，為將來打算。結果我因為證據不足，不能將我還押，所以可以保釋離開。但原來這還不是最差的情況...<br />\n那時候我明白到一直從小長大的家已經不再安全，我決定離開我的家人，搬離那個一直陪我長大的地方。過了一個月後，我回到警署報到的時候，有兩名警察帶我進了一個房間，一直出言恐嚇我，要求我轉做污點證人，還威脅我，聲稱我不轉做污點證人，會陷害我家人和朋友令他們坐監，那時我知道我要離開香港，這個我長大的地方，擁有我一切的地方。<br />\n這個是我的經歷，我知道我有多個隊友的經歷比我更加悽慘。但其實還有數以千計類似我們的情況，有很多人直到現在還沒有走出心理陰影。大家可能這一年看過大多同類型的事件，麻木了，導致有些需要被關注的手足被忽略了。其實還有很多被捕手足和無名義士需要各界去關注，希望大家不要只關注一些比較有名氣的人，而遺忘其他手足曾經的付出。<br />\n<br />\nNever lose hope.<br />\nTomorrow could be the day you&rsquo;ve been waiting for.<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nWebsite:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rsinternationals.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rsinternationals.com%2F&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7KF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=8fd22f03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rsinternationals.com/</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RSInternational-106544101050232/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRSInternational-106544101050232%2F&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7KF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=a4c57fce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RSInternational-106544101050232/</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram:<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/_rs.international\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2F_rs.international&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7KF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=ae2c4e69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/_rs.international</a><br />\n<br />\nTelegram:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/dragonslayerbrigade\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdragonslayerbrigade&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7KF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=e384c7a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/dragonslayerbrigade</a><br />\n#rsinternational"},{"pid":"8fdf9d5dc56822bcc9e2acc7b003a08ca553a2c7","tid":2316299,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T19:34:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff2e81567a0903582d3a2491cdc0cf350b0e6731","tid":2316299,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fdf9d5dc56822bcc9e2acc7b003a08ca553a2c7","tid":2316299,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T19:34:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T19:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62d7ce36057b9753f6f88f7d3f948b161608bbc","tid":2316299,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T19:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9860b2c40a4814197e4461a965d500840e7ad2d","tid":2316299,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T19:37:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7053f35d22336034962983c5f909217321098e3b","tid":2316299,"uid":79117,